{"type": "article", "id": 22876, "title": "北欧式 Bollo 椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-26T07:30:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110808sd3fw1gPIURJFNHi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是挪威设计师 Andreas Engesvik 在斯德哥尔摩家具展上带来的 Bollo 椅子，靠背、扶手和座位都是略带圆形的软垫，经过有意夸大，在细金属结构的对比下给人舒适的视觉感受。每种靠垫的中间都缝制了一根线，让靠垫的凹凸感强调其柔软。也是一款简约实用的北欧设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110805MJ9lCKdXVoDk6RTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110806tVihvxT2rpE3MCgu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67200855\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110806rqocj3MCmyY7Fl6G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110807hcdmWpKk0ePJRgj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23397436\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110807FJLYpMSrk0Ix8oa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06737968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}